original_title: W奴● 渚みつき/涼美ほのか
overview: It is "Mitsuki" and "Honoka" who are good friends and begging for metamorphosis training in Dogeza. He is an obedient servant who flutters his hips and raises a voice of joy even if his face is trampled with his feet. Anyway, the radical training play of the owner's husband started today for two female dogs who would be jealous if they weren't together.
tagline: "I will do anything for my husband..."
title: Double Sluts Mitsuki Nagisa/Honoka Suzumi
